{"tid":394350,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日早餐 舒芙蕾蛋","createTime":"2017-09-10T01:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T10:42:51.000Z","uid":18117,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a36aed41223905da80f58a27a07cf3f552e3a1b5","tid":394350,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T01:29:20.000Z","msg":"近排睇食戟之靈 見主角整既舒芙蕾蛋好吸引<br />\n震下震下咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/091854_61d18ec7b67d256d0f46901d0bebaa44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F091854_61d18ec7b67d256d0f46901d0bebaa44.jpg&h=ffa610ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次衰左 火太猛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/091852_f6623fba73f81d5b277fa1897684a3bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F091852_f6623fba73f81d5b277fa1897684a3bb.jpg&h=cdbba233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今個轉用細火煎焗兩分鐘 <br />\n好好食 一放入口會化開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過上碟果陣明明好靚 一陣間就扁哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/091853_61d18ec7b67d256d0f46901d0bebaa44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F091853_61d18ec7b67d256d0f46901d0bebaa44.jpg&h=0a53e949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食蛋食到飽 下次再試點整先唔會扁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9bc44e7c345b80946d93e3b5fe24738d430ab3","tid":394350,"uid":65587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T01:47:58.000Z","msg":"屌 一見到製成品笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ab810d2f540b49d61c5619cdde8a5cb9b82f26","tid":394350,"uid":104669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:02:02.000Z","msg":"果撻醬好醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7468ac65d86ad85a707689c436289615d8be899a","tid":394350,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 一見到製成品笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4186d806330b9b40e91c40edb8a3a73f5f4bc4","tid":394350,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果撻醬好醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用茄汁頂住檔先 費事為左兩隻蛋專登煮個汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0a81898034b17f6c1622d4f8ec18ce1b4951f1","tid":394350,"uid":3068,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:26:00.000Z","msg":"疏芙喱下話？"},{"pid":"e62d9f247fb6032166439d94a598db9e4598f6fa","tid":394350,"uid":60333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:26:38.000Z","msg":"創真後尾都係因為擺得耐扁左先出事<br />\n好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c0e39b49ac97888ee4f39f9b22afc7703e4bc3","tid":394350,"uid":97250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"點整？"},{"pid":"88a0121bbe4d7f3c3276901e8f3fe4b01cc7cdd1","tid":394350,"uid":18117,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:29:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>疏芙喱下話？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">舒芙蕾（法語：souffl&eacute;），又譯梳乎厘、梳芙厘[a]</span>，或稱作蛋奶酥，是一種源自法國的甜品，經烘焙後質輕而蓬鬆。主要材料包括蛋黃及經打勻後的蛋白。Souffl&eacute;一字來自法語中一個動詞souffler的過去分詞，意思是「使充氣」或簡單地指「蓬鬆地脹起來」－恰如其分地描述烘焙當兒蛋白與奶黃結合時的情況。雖然這多是甜品，但可以以起司或馬鈴薯變成正餐鹹味版本。"},{"pid":"286993f1d2f8f95cbcc2395ac5ce6abcc7053766","tid":394350,"uid":133750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:30:00.000Z","msg":"正皮比地獄強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539178b72592243bf278c7fa3a481de32befc0f4","tid":394350,"uid":18117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:33:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>創真後尾都係因為擺得耐扁左先出事<br />\n好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢擺得耐先出事 但我果個既形狀只係維持左十秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6448701bd6a94af3d4d113a2935d5d181a5a7980","tid":394350,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:37:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點整？</blockquote><br />\n同整蛋糕差唔多<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NaOMgu4LCww\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNaOMgu4LCww&d=kZkDW%2BfZm5qyW1XJEIC9C26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=390ab07c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NaOMgu4LCww</a><br />\nyoutube好多教學 隨便搵都有"},{"pid":"f972f12182de03f92f7b73ac0f9e5a7719caaacf","tid":394350,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T02:39:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正皮比地獄強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n落完地獄上番天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874c3bb4017b7ee589f2a22386e057a54ca62c8e","tid":394350,"uid":100015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:03:39.000Z","msg":"咁似m記d示範圖"},{"pid":"79e08ea91f864051153bde5cbfd1fb8a5ae33f5b","tid":394350,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T04:19:03.000Z","msg":"燶咗嗰舊好似好香口好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822740e0980c0d3f44f2c90715cb807a1ae6f09a","tid":394350,"uid":51250,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T04:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>疏芙喱下話？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">舒芙蕾（法語：souffl&eacute;），又譯梳乎厘、梳芙厘[a]</span>，或稱作蛋奶酥，是一種源自法國的甜品，經烘焙後質輕而蓬鬆。主要材料包括蛋黃及經打勻後的蛋白。Souffl&eacute;一字來自法語中一個動詞souffler的過去分詞，意思是「使充氣」或簡單地指「蓬鬆地脹起來」－恰如其分地描述烘焙當兒蛋白與奶黃結合時的情況。雖然這多是甜品，但可以以起司或馬鈴薯變成正餐鹹味版本。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港係叫梳芙厘，台灣先叫舒乜柒。"},{"pid":"78e2ca47088f9156bd9b56236aa71ae37b571667","tid":394350,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:14:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>疏芙喱下話？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">舒芙蕾（法語：souffl&eacute;），又譯梳乎厘、梳芙厘[a]</span>，或稱作蛋奶酥，是一種源自法國的甜品，經烘焙後質輕而蓬鬆。主要材料包括蛋黃及經打勻後的蛋白。Souffl&eacute;一字來自法語中一個動詞souffler的過去分詞，意思是「使充氣」或簡單地指「蓬鬆地脹起來」－恰如其分地描述烘焙當兒蛋白與奶黃結合時的情況。雖然這多是甜品，但可以以起司或馬鈴薯變成正餐鹹味版本。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港係叫梳芙厘，台灣先叫舒乜柒。</blockquote><br />\n舒芙蕾個名靚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4a49fc97de51d17a5d5bc98f165f5da75054b4","tid":394350,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>燶咗嗰舊好似好香口好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係垃圾筒 執番比你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c5edcbf384975da20a803535238895887b9b0b","tid":394350,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}